text: Announcer: Settle down, settle down!
Announcer: Welcome Psykers, to the 100th ==Psycho Killer Annual Convention==!
Psykers: Woooooooooooooo!!!
Announcer: Give a round of applause to our special guest tonight!
Announcer: We all know how hard each of you have worked this year, and we congratulate you. As a way to give back to the community, we have organized a packed programme for you tonight.
Not least our special guest, the internationally acclaimed, Fine Art Grant Prix recipient, highly regarded, artist of the year: {0} !
Psykers: WooooOOOOoooOOOooooO !!!
Announcer: Our guest of honor will delight us by the end of tonight's festivities, with the ==Mask of Centuries==, an art piece that will be created during the course of this night, with your help.
Psykers: WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO !!!
Announcer: {0} is well known for their artisanal mask creation practice, though their methods remain obscure. Please enjoy the buffet and welcome our first performer ==FADEOUT==
